Summary: saw a landing filed etched out in green chalk that had a lot of chairs for viewing out in the woods
divs: Sighting Details many years ago i saw something as i still wonder today, i saw no object but a marked off landing area for something. This was in a wooded area where i noticed a chalked in what looked like a landing pad for something. The chalk was all in green as there were chairs seated in front of a stage. I thought something very small may have landed, as i noticed that Mercury was high in the 5 am morning sky.
